Target: `module/LLMWorkflow/ingestion/parsers/GeometryNodesParser.ps1`

Reason:
- stop silently swallowing JSON probe failures during input-type detection
- stop silently swallowing JSON fallback failures in blend-text parsing

---

## Patch A: surface JSON probe failure in `Detect-GeometryNodesInputType`

Replace:

```powershell
if (($trimmed.StartsWith('{') -and $trimmed.EndsWith('}')) -or
    ($trimmed.StartsWith('[') -and $trimmed.EndsWith(']'))) {
    try {
        $null = $trimmed | ConvertFrom-Json -ErrorAction Stop
        return 'Json'
    }
    catch {
    }
}
```

With:

```powershell
if (($trimmed.StartsWith('{') -and $trimmed.EndsWith('}')) -or
    ($trimmed.StartsWith('[') -and $trimmed.EndsWith(']'))) {
    try {
        $null = $trimmed | ConvertFrom-Json -ErrorAction Stop
        return 'Json'
    }
    catch {
        Write-Verbose "[GeometryNodesParser] JSON probe failed during input-type detection: $($_.Exception.Message)"
    }
}
```

## Patch B: surface JSON fallback failure in `Parse-GeometryNodesFromBlendText`

Replace:

```powershell
if (($trimmed.StartsWith('{') -and $trimmed.EndsWith('}')) -or
    ($trimmed.StartsWith('[') -and $trimmed.EndsWith(']'))) {
    try {
        return Parse-GeometryNodesFromJson -JsonContent $TextContent
    }
    catch {
    }
}
```

With:

```powershell
if (($trimmed.StartsWith('{') -and $trimmed.EndsWith('}')) -or
    ($trimmed.StartsWith('[') -and $trimmed.EndsWith(']'))) {
    try {
        return Parse-GeometryNodesFromJson -JsonContent $TextContent
    }
    catch {
        Write-Verbose "[GeometryNodesParser] Blend-text JSON parse failed, falling back to Python-style parsing: $($_.Exception.Message)"
    }
}
```
